race.comment: INTRODUCED (2) is mixing form and out of the placings last time but was a Grade 5 winner three starts ago and moves to Box 2 this time where she has performed well. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. COMPUTER MAN (7) has been in super consistent form recently with three minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (22.26) at this track. Has the ability to give this a shake. MASKED RIOT (8) is a handy dog who jumped from box 3 last time out and scored by a neck at this track (22.06). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Leading chance again. MASON KAI (1) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.
